			<item>
				<title>Project Log: The Sunflower Crochet Bouquet Blanket</title>
				<link>http://localhost:1313/hobbies/sunflower-blanket/</link>
				<pubDate>Sat, 27 Jun 2026 16:00:00 -0500</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:1313/hobbies/sunflower-blanket/</guid>
				<description>&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/sunflower_flat.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;flat&#34; width=&#34;100%&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-vision--blueprint&#34;&gt;The Vision &amp;amp; Blueprint&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The goal of this project is to create a textured throw blanket using worsted weight yarn. Instead of traditional stripes, it’s built out of modular motifs that form a sunflower bouquet patchwork.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;color-palette&#34;&gt;Color Palette&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Petals:&lt;/strong&gt; Mustard / Goldenrod Yellow&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Centers:&lt;/strong&gt; Espresso / Dark Brown&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Background &amp;amp; Border:&lt;/strong&gt; Sage Green and Cream&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;materials--specs&#34;&gt;Materials &amp;amp; Specs&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Yarn:&lt;/strong&gt; Worsted weight acrylic (for durability and easy washing)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hook Size:&lt;/strong&gt; 5.0 mm (H-8) to keep the stitches relatively tight but soft&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Final Dimensions:&lt;/strong&gt; Target is 50&amp;quot; x 60&amp;quot; (roughly 80 individual square motifs)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;instructions&#34;&gt;Instructions&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;coming&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
